Package: ggpostpamr
Type: Package
Title: Modern ggplot2 Graphs for PAMR Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Christophe Desterke
Maintainer: Christophe Desterke <christophe.desterke@gmail.com>
Description: Provides modern and customizable ggplot2-based visualizations 
    for PAMR (Prediction Analysis for Microarrays) results. 
    Includes several functions to explore and display PAMR outputs 
    in a publication-ready format.
